sources.title: PAW Patrol's Dark Secret, Explained
sources.description: Original: https://youtu.be/rwhUpu9MfZ0 https://web.archive.org/web/20220910172523/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rwhUpu9MfZ0&feature=youtu.be The description says: PAW Patrol is a TV show for kids. It's very popular, so we might as well ask: "What vision of policing does it suggest?" PAW Patrol is also a very bad TV show.
